title: Dr. Katrina Johnson
text:
Welcome!
Thanks for stopping by my internet neighborhood. I’m glad to have you join me. This website is intended as a place to share material for class activities.


Education
PhD in Applied Mathematics (2018), University of Utah
MS in Mathematics (2012), University of Utah
BS in Mathematics/Statistics - Composite Teaching (2007), Utah State University
BA in Liberal Arts and Sciences (2005), Utah State University
AAT in Computer Aided Drafting and Design (2005), Utah College of Applied Technology
